               <p>On Monday the 5th of this month, near six o'clock in the evening, going down <placeName id="t17840114-56-crimeloc305">Ludgate Hill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17840114-56-crimeloc305" type="placeName" value="Ludgate Hill"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17840114-56-crimeloc305" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840114-56-off303 t17840114-56-crimeloc305"></join>, I was called to by two gentlemen, who told me the prisoner had picked my pocket; I immediately turned back, they had then hold of the prisoner, and I saw them take from him my pocket handkerchief, the constable has the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>(The handkerchief produced.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was going to Ludgate Hill, and I saw this handkerchief lay on the ground, I picked it up, and was running towards this gentleman.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840114-56-verdict306" type="verdictDescription">
